&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Pay Transparency:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The base pay for this role is: $192,000 - $252,000 per year. You are also eligible for employee benefits, participation in Oscar&#39;s unlimited vacation program, company equity grants, and annual performance bonuses.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
