&lt;li&gt;Actively identifies and reduces failure domains while working with their team to do the same.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Builds software to minimize effort and business impact during maintenance and failures.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Guide the development of Service-Level Objectives (SLOs) for systems they and their team are responsible for.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Compliance with all applicable laws and regulations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Other duties as assigned&lt;/li&gt;
